{
  "texts": [
    "However, capturing the level of persuasiveness from argumentative essays is not a simple task.",
    "The use of discourse elements in argumentative essay demonstrated the capability of picking organization quality features (Song et al. 2020a).",
    "In a similar manner, Hicke et al. (2023) utilizes discourse element features to identify persuasive sections in argumentative essay.",
    "They employed DeBERTa for a robust essay representation.",
    "Each token from this representation is scored its level of effectiveness in its corresponding discourse element."
  ]
}